    <summary>HP 3D DriveGuard provides protection for a notebook computer's internal disk drive if the computer is accidentally dropped or abruptly hits another object</summary>
    <description>This will install HP 3D DriveGuard, which provides protection for a notebook computer's internal disk drive if the computer is accidentally dropped or abruptly hits another object. This package is available on supported notebooks with supported operating systems.
	
Fixes
- Fixes an issue where a system using a micro-SATA (mSATA) disk drive with Intel Rapid Start Technology enabled stops functioning properly (hangs) when the system enters sleep mode (S3).</description>
